&lt;li&gt;Both, on and off campus housing options are available.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;But most of the students prefer in campus as the hostels and mess food is way better than other colleges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

6@***@&lt;ul&gt;
