&lt;/ul&gt;

6@***@&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Separate hostel facilities for both girls and boys.There are total 17 boys hostels and 6 girls hostels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hostels are spacious and well designed and attached with the&amp;nbsp;mess.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Students have an option of choosing his/her desired mess.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1)South Indian (VEG/NON-VEG).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2)North Indian (VEG/NON-VEG).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3)Special mess. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;of various catering services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quality of food is best&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;From second year onwards &amp;nbsp;room is allotted based upon CGPA of all semester.Different kinds of rooms are available for students.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1)6 BED(AC/NON-AC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2)4 BED(AC/NON-AC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3)2 BED(AC/NON-AC) etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Students are allowed to watch tv whenever they want but not during exams time and night time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hostel rules are little strict for first-year students,and all students should give biometric attendance during night time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For first-year girls, the outing will be restricted for 3 months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;After that, a 2-hour outing will be given daily.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A maximum of 6-hour outing on Saturday and Sunday that too with parents permission.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

6@***@&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;On the&amp;nbsp;campus, hostels are nice and good by hostel standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Food is surprisingly good but you can get bored after a certain point of time for which enough options are there in and around campus covering everything from Indian to Chinese food.&lt;/li&gt;
